@startuml
title FHIR Service Write Operation

participant "App" as app
participant "FHIR Service" as fhir
participant "Pod" as pod

app->fhir: 1. PUT /Observation/123
activate fhir

fhir->fhir: 2. Validate against\nWellData profile

fhir->fhir: 3. Update in-memory store\n& search indices

fhir->pod: 4. PUT .ttl file\n(/weare/fhir/Observation/123.ttl)
activate pod
pod-->fhir: 5. 200 OK
deactivate pod

fhir-->app: 6. 200 OK\n(FHIR OperationOutcome)
deactivate fhir

@enduml
